sections.heading: of State Governments declared a joint governmental agency
sections.text: The Council of State Governments is declared to be a joint governmental agency of this state and of the other states which cooperate through it.SourceLaws 1937, c. 110, ยง 9, p. 409;C.S.Supp.,1941, ยง 81-7309;R.S.1943, ยง 81-824.
